@deffn {Macro} rest-server:with-api api &body body
@findex rest-server:with-api
Execute body under api scope.
   Example:
   (with-api test-api
      (define-api-function get-user :get (:url-prefix "users/@{id@}")
                                    '((:id :integer))))
@end deffn
